  "task": {
    "task_id": "202605132134-E6RDJG",
    "title": "Fix evaluator root-resolution error surfacing (issue #3655)",
    "intent": "GitHub issue: https://github.com/basilisk-labs/agentplane/issues/3655\n\nSummary: evaluator list/show can swallow resolveProject failures and silently fall back to builtin-only mode, hiding project evaluators from .agentplane/evaluators/*.md.\n\nAcceptance criteria (from issue):\n- Running evaluator commands from a repository subdirectory can locate the project root or emits an explicit root-resolution error.\n- Builtin-only fallback is used only for intentional no-project contexts, not for swallowed resolveProject failures.\n- Regression coverage verifies project evaluator IDs remain visible from subdirectories or fail with a clear diagnostic.\n\nPointers: packages/agentplane/src/commands/evaluator/evaluator.command.ts; review discussion linked in issue.",
    "requested_by": {
      "type": "agentplane_role",
      "id": "ORCHESTRATOR"
    }
  },
